          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Fighting for Intelligent, Rational, and Ethical Dismissal Act or the FIRED Act</b></p> <p>This bill limits the circumstances under which the President may remove the Director of the Federal Bureau of Investigation&mdash;specifically, for inefficiency, neglect of duty, or malfeasance.</p>]]></text>
